      <div class="s4-sp-header">
        <span class="s4-sp-eyebrow">Infrastructure &amp; partners</span>
        <h2 class="s4-sp-title">Our sponsors.</h2>
        <p class="s4-sp-sub">The organisations that power and support Ubuntu Budgie.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="s4-sp-grid">

        <div class="s4-sp-card">
          <img class="s4-sp-logo" src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/f/ff/DigitalOcean_logo.svg" alt="DigitalOcean" />
