          <p class="s4-sp-label">Infrastructure</p>
          <p class="s4-sp-desc">Deployment, management and scaling of our infrastructure.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="s4-sp-card">
          <img class="s4-sp-logo" src="icons/discourse.png" alt="Discourse" />
          <div class="s4-sp-divider"></div>
          <p class="s4-sp-label">Community Forum</p>
          <p class="s4-sp-desc">Civilized discussion for our community about Ubuntu Budgie development.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</div>